!! How to use 如何使用

You can resize the tab block to be narrower so there can be two columns of tab blocks. And you can resize the sidebar (using [[Resizable Sidebar|https://talk.tiddlywiki.org/t/resizable-sidebar-resize-your-sidebar-with-mouse-dragging/1740]]) so you get more space for more columns. 

你可以调整标签页瓷砖的大小，使其更小，这样就可以有两列标签页瓷砖了。而且你可以调整侧边栏的大小(使用[[可调整的侧边栏插件（Resizable Sidebar）|https://talk.tiddlywiki.org/t/resizable-sidebar-resize-your-sidebar-with-mouse-dragging/1740]])，来放下更多的列。
